1
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:32,880
(Episode 17)

2
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,720
Xiaomeng is a gentle and pretty girl.

3
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,240
She is a fine girl.

4
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,520
Am I not?

5
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,400
Chairman Zhou,

6
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,720
I don't expect too much.

7
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,720
I only want you to give me a chance.

8
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:04,560
Compile and analyze the data on Luofeng,

9
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,000
and identify the consumer groups.

10
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,440
Be meticulous and precise.

11
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,480
Yes.

12
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,320
Good morning, Chairman Zhou.

13
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,800
Did you sleep well?

14
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,440
The room was very comfortable,

15
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:54,120
but when I lay down,
I could only think of the project.

16
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,200
So I simply got up and made some changes.

17
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,320
Opportunities are for
those who come prepared.

18
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,800
I believe today will end well.

19
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,960
Tie up your hair.
It'll make you look refreshed.

20
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,280
Really?

21
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,200
Let's eat.

22
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:25,600
The development of stadiums
is the latest craze.

23
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,200
We want to build not just a stadium,

24
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,800
but an industrial chain.

25
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:33,720
It will be a habitat system that
integrates sports, business, and leisure.

26
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,920
This is what Shenghai does best.

27
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:39,160
Visitors will get full satisfaction
and enjoyment here.

28
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:42,840
This is our concept of
a commercially integrated stadium.

29
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,480
Wonderful.

30
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,040
-Wonderful.
-Wonderful.

31
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,840
-Impressive!
-Great!

32
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,400
This is really impressive.

33
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,440
-Yes!
-Great!

34
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,640
President Jiang.

35
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:07,520
I did not expect this kid
to be so well prepared today.

36
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,080
However, it's not going to be so simple.

37
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:14,200
Let him be complacent for a few days.

38
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,400
Keep an eye on his tender offer,

39
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:20,000
especially his bottom price.

40
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,400
Report to me promptly.

41
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,680
Why?

42
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,080
Shouldn't this be strictly confidential
from our rivals?

43
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,240
I have my own plan.

44
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:32,120
Are you trying to take over Shenghai

45
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,480
or destroy it?

46
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,840
Do not second-guess me.

47
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,440
Guang,

48
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,120
I want to see Xiaomeng.

49
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,320
Drive me to the harbor straight away.

50
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,600
Have you made up your mind?

51
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,680
What else can I do?

52
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,240
♪A sudden crack♪

53
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:41,520
♪Got on my nerves and caused me pain♪

54
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:45,000
♪Everything has become pale to me♪

55
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:47,920
♪Diving with my happiness♪

56
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:54,280
♪Into the void that you left behind♪

57
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:57,320
♪Our silent and broken past♪

58
00:05:57,400 --> 00:06:00,240
♪Is awaiting you to touch it
Once in a while♪

59
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,920
♪Take back my heart♪

60
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,480
♪Take back my soul♪

61
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,080
♪Don't make me cry♪

62
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,640
♪And leave me in sadness♪

63
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,080
♪There is a parallel♪

64
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,000
♪Universe of love♪

65
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:13,280
♪To make up for lost time♪

66
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,960
♪Take back my heart♪

67
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,520
♪Take back my soul♪

68
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,960
♪Don't make me cry♪

69
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,640
♪Let me confess♪

70
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,000
♪There is a parallel♪

71
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,960
♪Button of love♪

72
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,120
♪Giving this moment a reason for love♪

73
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:29,400
♪Because I love you♪

74
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:43,400
♪Believe in a mirror image
That completes my life♪

75
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:46,240
♪And fill up what we have missed♪

76
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,400
♪My left cheek♪

77
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:52,200
♪Is transformed
By the rolling teardrops into♪

78
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,840
(Resignation Letter)

79
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,520
(Nanyue Broadcasting Company)

80
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,080
Xiaomeng!

81
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,800
Xiaomeng!

82
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,600
Come back with me.

83
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,040
I don't want to.

84
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,360
You can't hide here forever.

85
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,800
Come back to Nanyue with me.

86
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,600
Let go! I don't want to go back!
I want to stay here.

87
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,560
-I don't want anyone to find me.
-For the last time,

88
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,800
pack up right now,
and catch the last ferry with me.

89
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,760
I don't want to.

90
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,640
Let's go see Miss Xiaomeng. Okay?

91
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,520
Haixing,

92
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,600
why are you here?

93
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:59,560
Miss Xiaomeng, please don't go.

94
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:02,160
Okay, I won't.

95
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:04,600
I'll stay and play with you. Okay?

96
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:09,320
Who is this?

97
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:12,840
Ms. Li, this is Yan.

98
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,800
I know about Yan.

99
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:18,560
He is the son of Uncle Fang's
former employer.

100
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:24,160
I heard you said you were leaving today.

101
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,200
I'm afraid today is not likely.

102
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:28,720
Fang just called and said that

103
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,440
all the vessels are at berth.

104
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,880
A typhoon is heading here.
You won't be able to leave today.

105
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:34,120
He can't even make it back either.

106
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,480
Does it mean the ferry here
will stop operating?

107
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,640
Yes.

108
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:49,080
Affected by the outer circulation
of Typhoon No. 30,

109
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,800
a sudden rainstorm has hit
the Daling Island waters,

110
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,560
with gust wind force
reaching Beaufort scale 11.

111
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,440
Many fishing vessels are affected.

112
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:56,600
We are not sure how many vessels
are affected.

113
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:59,600
Over the next few days, heavy rain
will continue in the Daling Island waters.

114
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,400
See? What did I say?

115
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:04,120
You definitely cannot leave today.
Why not tomorrow?

116
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:07,440
In view of the wind and heavy downpours
that Typhoon Doksuri might bring,

117
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:09,600
all the cities and counties
in the province are on high alert,

118
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,600
and doing the best to protect themselves.

119
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,040
This is Uncle Fang's room.

120
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,320
You have to stay here for the night.

121
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,920
Uncle Fang sees you as his family.

122
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,640
When he comes back tomorrow,
see him before you leave.

123
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:37,240
How about you? Will you go back with me?

124
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,200
We should get some rest now.

125
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:44,160
Do you feel that you have
suffered injustice?

126
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,320
It's not like that.

127
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,040
Then why did you leave without telling me?

128
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,280
Do you still think that
I posted the photos online?

129
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,720
Why don't you believe me?

130
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,840
I do not know,

131
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,320
and I do not want to know.

132
00:09:56,960 --> 00:10:00,040
I only know that everyone in Nanyue
has seen those photos.

133
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,520
When I walk on the street,

134
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,480
everyone is staring and judging me.

135
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:07,040
Some parents even
won't let me near their children.

136
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,680
They are afraid I am a bad influence.

137
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,240
Has it ever occurred to them

138
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,520
that I am also a victim?

139
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,200
So you hide yourself

140
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,640
to evade all these things,

141
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,000
like an ostrich

142
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,400
that hides its head in the sand
when there is danger?

143
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,840
Can that solve any problem?

144
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,360
Yan,

145
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,040
I just want to calm down by myself
for a few days.

146
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,720
It doesn't mean I don't want to go back.

147
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,440
You hide whenever you have a problem.

148
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,280
You hide away for a few days this time.
What about next time?

149
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,960
What would you do next time?

150
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,480
Will you leave without
telling anyone again?

151
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:35,320
Will you leave the Zhou family and me?

152
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,760
I...

153
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,760
I just don't know...

154
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,240
how to face you.

155
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,840
What about your mother?

156
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,280
Don't you care whether she lives or dies?

157
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,640
My mother...

158
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,160
How is my mother now?

159
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,200
As long as you stay with me,

160
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,240
your mother will be safe.

161
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,200
Xiaomeng...

162
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:06,280
you can't solve your problem by hiding.

163
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:09,240
It will only make matters worse.

164
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,240
All things aside,

165
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,840
as you and I are both responsible
for Shenghai's reputation.

166
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,360
surely we have a heavier burden
than average person.

167
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,960
You are not a little girl anymore.

168
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:21,320
You know what you should do
and what you should not.

169
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:23,200
Go back and think about it.

170
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,560
I've got your point.

171
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:29,920
You may leave now.

172
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,760
Zhou Yanzhao actually went to
look for Xiaomeng.

173
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:50,480
At a time when the Luofeng project
needed him most,

174
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,960
he left.

175
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,840
Now I finally realize

176
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,480
how important Zhou Xiaomeng is to him.

177
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:07,040
Well, so you're drowning your sorrow
with alcohol?

178
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,600
Mind your own business.

179
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,800
Miss Sun,

180
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,720
I want to encourage you

181
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,200
to court Zhou Yanzhao.

182
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:17,960
What do you mean?

183
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,560
Nothing.

184
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,360
I just think you still have a shot.

185
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,000
If I have a shot,

186
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,960
you will have the chance
to secure your target too. Yes?

187
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,760
She is different.

188
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,280
How so?

189
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,200
I used to think women are all the same.

190
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,240
They live for their men.

191
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,080
You only have to move a finger,

192
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,080
and they know what you mean.

193
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:53,000
They are as tame as kittens,
domesticated by you.

194
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,560
I am happy when I am with them

195
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,760
because I can control everything.

196
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:02,080
But some woman

197
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:04,120
just has to glance at you,

198
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,360
and you will fall deeply for her.

199
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,880
You can't extricate yourself.

200
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,720
You can even feel lost.

201
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,640
However, there is a
dangerous person by her side.

202
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,680
He is her guardian.

203
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,160
You can't even get near her.

204
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,000
Be careful. He might counterattack.

205
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,520
Don't you know that

206
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,440
I love challenges?

207
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:32,960
Tell me,

208
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,640
what you like about Zhou Yanzhao.

209
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,760
What do I like about him?

210
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,560
He is calm and collected.

211
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:48,720
He is smart and decisive in his work.

212
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:56,120
Maybe it is his unfathomable eyes,

213
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:58,360
and his self-assured composure.

214
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,040
I can't figure it out.

215
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,200
I only know that
I'm one step away from him,

216
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,560
but we are worlds apart.

217
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:08,320
I do not know what he is thinking.

218
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,320
After the incident in his family,

219
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,840
he has become a different man.

220
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,080
He never shows his emotions.

221
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:19,840
He isolates himself with indifference,
and works like crazy.

222
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:24,000
He seems to be venting
all his emotions on his work.

223
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:31,280
Are you saying Zhou Yanzhao
was different before?

224
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:34,560
Many things are not
as simple as they look.

225
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,480
After you gradually get to know him,

226
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,080
you will understand.

227
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,840
Ms. Li, are the noodles
for table five ready?

228
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:18,000
Oh, no,

229
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,600
I'm sorry, Xiaomeng.

230
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:20,760
It's okay.

231
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,920
-Your seafood noodles.
-Thank you.

232
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:28,040
Here you go. Your seafood noodles.

233
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,440
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

234
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,240
Xiaomeng!

235
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,600
Xiaomeng!

236
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:23,000
I have to answer a call.

237
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,360
Hello.

238
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,080
Where are you? Why aren't you here?

239
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,440
I did not go anywhere.

240
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,720
I thought that the typhoon is coming,

241
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,280
and the tourists are stranded.

242
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,240
Ms. Li's noodle house will be very busy,

243
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,720
so I came to help her.

244
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,400
Stay in the house
if there's nothing to go out for.

245
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,480
Don't go out all the time.

246
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,600
I understand. I'll be back soon.

247
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,840
Xiaomeng, is that Yan?

248
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:57,560
He is already tracking you with his phone
this early in the morning.

249
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,040
He is afraid that you'll leave him.

250
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:01,360
Ms. Li, what are you talking about?

251
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:04,080
Is Yan your boyfriend?

252
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:08,280
It's complicated between me and Yan.

253
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:09,840
We are only--

254
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,520
I can tell.

255
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:13,280
Even if you two are not an item,

256
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:15,120
I'm sure you both like each other.

257
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,880
I do not know whether he likes me or not.

258
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:22,240
If he really likes me,

259
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:24,840
why is he always hurting me?

260
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:30,040
Xiaomeng, although I do not know

261
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,400
what happened between you two,

262
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:33,120
one who's involved too deeply
might not be able to see clear.

263
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:35,760
As an onlooker, I'd like to remind you.

264
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,520
If he does not truly like you,

265
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:40,000
he will not come looking for you,

266
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:43,640
much less repeatedly ask you
to go back with him.

267
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:58,560
Yan. I'm back.

268
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,480
Yan.

269
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:03,680
Yan.

270
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:07,840
Yan.

271
