449
00:31:18,080 --> 00:31:19,960
It's you who should be hating me.

450
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:21,880
It's okay. You can hate me.

451
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:24,400
No.

452
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:26,680
I have never hated you.

453
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:33,440
In fact, I've often forgot

454
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:37,440
the hurt and hatred between us.

455
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,240
Yan,

456
00:31:41,520 --> 00:31:43,720
I really want to return to the past.

457
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,400
Don't move.

458
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,240
Are you still scared?

459
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,640
Not anymore.

460
