489
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,000
It was about your mother.

490
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:47,000
What happened to my mother?

491
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:50,680
The doctor said
she had basic response to external sound.

492
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,080
Really?

493
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:54,520
That's great news!

494
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:05,320
If she regains consciousness,

495
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,880
