496
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,760
will come to a conclusion.

497
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:13,240
Yan, it's not like that.

498
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,960
Whatever the outcome,

499
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,960
