509
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,360
I will.

510
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:05,000
Haixing, I am glad and thankful
for your companionship

511
00:35:05,040 --> 00:35:06,440
over the last few days.

512
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:10,280
