and have a little more patience.

523
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:37,280
Ms. Li,

524
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:40,160
I know what you mean.

525
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:42,600
Don't worry. I will be okay.

526
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,240
Till we meet again.

527
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:46,120
Okay. Go quickly,

528
00:35:46,200 --> 00:35:49,200
or your bossy chairman
will call and ask you to hurry up.

529
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:52,120
Okay. Goodbye, Ms. Li.

