544
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:54,000
and has been having a high fever since.

545
00:36:54,120 --> 00:36:56,480
The villagers are using this as an excuse
to stop us from carrying on.

546
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,160
I'm trying to negotiate with them.

547
00:36:58,240 --> 00:36:59,360
It is very difficult.

548
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:01,320
Now that I heard of Xiaomeng being fine,

549
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,800
my fighting spirit is rekindled.

550
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:03,960
That's enough.

551
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,720
I'm going back to the company right now.
Wait for my news.

552
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,160
Go to Shenghai Group first.

553
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:13,160
Then drive Xiaomeng to the hospital.

554
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,720
I admire you, Yan.

555
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:17,240
Why?

556
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,800
Your life is so exhausting.

557
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,960
Just drive and stop talking.

558
00:37:35,240 --> 00:37:36,360
Exactly what happened?

559
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,960
Initially they agreed to the road repair.

560
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:40,160
On the very first day,
they made trouble at the site.

561
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:42,560
They claimed that a girl
was scared out of her wits.

562
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:44,520
It's obvious that they are being
deliberately unreasonable.

563
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,000
Any progress?

564
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:55,440
No matter what we said,
they wouldn't let us start work.

565
00:37:55,680 --> 00:37:57,480
Have you found out
what the exact reason is?

566
00:37:57,560 --> 00:37:59,200
The little girl is really sick,

567
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:02,000
but this has nothing to do
with our road repair.

568
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,720
It is utter nonsense.

569
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:05,760
I heard the villagers said

570
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,520
that they would rather

571
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:09,480
have another company
to develop Eco-tourism here.

572
00:38:10,200 --> 00:38:11,920
I'm not really sure about this.

573
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,160
Hold on.

574
00:38:13,240 --> 00:38:14,320
Wait.

575
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:18,280
Qingyan, go to the Marketing Department,

576
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,840
and find out which company
has a project in Yunnan.

577
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:24,320
By the way, do Shenghai have
a charity foundation?

578
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:25,640
Yes.

579
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:28,760
There are only two possibilities.

580
00:38:29,200 --> 00:38:32,120
First, the village benefits more
from another company,

581
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:33,200
so they've reneged.

582
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:35,920
Second, another incident
happened in the village,

583
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,320
and the villagers had to renege.

584
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:39,120
First, find out which is true,

585
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:41,440
and immediately send for the person
in charge of the charity foundation.

586
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:43,600
We'll take care of the incident
about the scared girl,

587
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,920
Okay. I've got it.

588
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:49,880
Jiang Ze,

589
00:38:50,240 --> 00:38:51,880
run a thorough investigation,

590
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:54,440
and find out exactly
why they won't let us repair the road.

591
00:38:54,520 --> 00:38:55,600
By the way,

592
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:57,080
pay attention to your own safety.

593
00:38:58,480 --> 00:39:00,160
If I could survive overseas,

594
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:02,400
the safe environment of my home country
is a piece of cake.

595
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:04,640
Don't worry about me dying.

596
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,640
Okay.

597
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,120
I'm hanging up.

598
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:20,320
(Xiaomeng)

599
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,760
Hello.

600
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:24,800
The number you dialed is not available.

601
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:33,360
I got it.

602
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:36,160
This company indeed has a Yunnan project

603
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:37,560
that involves this village.

604
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:40,080
However, the company is rather small,
and doesn't have much business.

605
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:41,080
Furthermore,

606
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:43,400
Their project is very vague too.

607
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:53,680
This is undoubtedly just a shell company.

608
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,640
It doesn't even have
a complete project document.

609
00:39:55,720 --> 00:39:57,880
How could it possibly
participate in the Yunnan project?

610
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:58,880
You're right.

611
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:01,520
Eco-tourism is certainly not
the reason it gets involved now.

612
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,680
It's not that simple.

613
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:05,640
-Go and investigate immediately.
-Yes. Right away.

614
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:13,760
-Hello.
-Chairman Zhou, I've found out why.

615
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:16,560
A few of the villagers
have caught a very serious illness.

616
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:18,000
and they need money for treatment.

617
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:19,160
A small company

618
00:40:19,200 --> 00:40:21,320
is acquiring land under the pretext
of developing Eco-tourism,

619
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,800
but is actually building
a commercial resort.

620
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:25,320
The villagers need money,
and want to cooperate with them.

621
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:27,480
The little girl just happened to get sick,

622
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:29,200
and they blamed it on the construction.

623
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,840
So this is what it is all about.

624
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:34,480
Lingxi, you and Ze negotiate with them.

625
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:36,600
We are willing to provide
the best medical team

626
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:38,000
to treat the villagers.

627
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:40,720
They should not renege
on what they've agreed.

628
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:43,400
Prepare a contract immediately
for the worst scenario.

629
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:45,400
Okay. I will do it as soon as possible.

630
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,840
Say hello to Xiaomeng for me.

631
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:50,720
Okay.

632
00:40:51,200 --> 00:40:52,840
Return here once you get something.

633
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,560
We have to go to Sydney soon.

634
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:56,800
Okay.

635
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,160
Chairman Zhou, do you want to see me?

636
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,080
-Please have a seat.
-Okay.

637
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,200
What are the medical projects

638
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,000
that our charity foundation have?

639
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:19,040
We have special Fund for Children's Health
for the city's welfare center.

640
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:21,120
A certain portion of the fund is reserved

641
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:23,120
for the old and young who are left behind
in poor mountain regions.

642
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:26,000
We have an urgent issue now.

643
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:29,160
Our company has a project in Yunnan
that cooperates with a village.

644
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,840
Many of the villagers have caught
a very serious illness.

645
00:41:31,640 --> 00:41:33,040
Find out what is the cause,

646
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:35,880
and intervene fully in the name
of the charity foundation.

647
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:36,800
Yes.

648
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:37,960
Remember.

649
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:40,560
Regardless of whether we can
settle the company's issue,

650
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:42,280
we must treat the illness.

651
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,760
Okay. I'll do it now.

652
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:12,160
The nurse said
when she was changing her clothes,

653
00:42:12,200 --> 00:42:14,320
your mother's hands twitched slightly.

654
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:17,760
She also responded a bit to loud noise.

655
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:22,640
Does it mean
my mother could wake up anytime soon?

656
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:24,320
Will she wake up today?

657
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:26,360
Relax, Xiaomeng.

658
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,040
Here's what's happening now.

659
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:29,560
Last month, Chairman Zhou suggested

660
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:32,560
we purchase equipment for
treatment plans from overseas.

661
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,600
I've talked to Dr. Xiao,

662
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:36,800
and the hospital has specially bought

663
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:39,560
one of the most advanced physiotherapy
equipment in the world at the moment.

664
00:42:39,640 --> 00:42:42,360
It's been treating Ye Sirong,
based on her daily condition.

665
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:48,800
The equipment has been purchased
according to Yan's proposal?

666
00:42:49,120 --> 00:42:50,160
Yes.

667
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,520
Why haven't you told me?

668
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:58,080
I've just been informed
upon returning to the hospital

669
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:00,160
that I'd be on the medical team
for treating Aunt Ye.

670
00:43:00,240 --> 00:43:03,480
I've also learned that it has imported
the latest equipment and technology.
